{"tid":1442084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【關於文宣】","createTime":"2019-08-10T22:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:49:47.000Z","uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3c5d4d500892207759ba0bac4d8fee2e7e34f9","tid":1442084,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:22:03.000Z","msg":"我直接講兩個大問題，你唔鍾意都係咁話。<br />\n<br />\n一，大部分文宣係無設計過，好撚差。咁咩係無設計過？就係你嘅目的唔清晰，target唔清晰，內容繁多散亂唔準確，無美學唔吸引。<br />\n<br />\n二，印刷費係好撚貴，地區連儂牆文宣要快，要多，我竟然見到有幾個post提及「印刷組」呢個詞，前線要籌資金捐資源，咁有無人諗過邊個俾錢做印刷？係咪你哋口中嘅「印刷組」自己俾曬，撳個制就有嘢出，紙同墨都唔洗錢？<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母香港人就成日話設計無用，仲夠膽死成日同藝術撈埋嚟講，睇吓你哋整張A4都搞唔撚掂，就知你哋喺設計同藝術方面係文盲，憨撚鳩。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n一<br />\n<br />\n每張propaganda只適宜講<span style=\"color: orange;\">一個訊息</span>，常見有幾類，批評政府，上屆活動，激勵士氣等等，內容包括圖片同埋文字用語，都要對準呢張嘢嘅受眾，姐係用佢鍾意睇嘅文字寫啊。<br />\n<br />\n我知你有好撚多嘢想話俾人聽，但事實係無人想睇咁多嘢，所以每類每次宜精簡不宜多，你可以一套三張咁貼，但每次出嚟都咁多字就898，你貼完都無人睇，仲會令人對連儂牆產生疲勞，所以唔該你諗清楚先好做。<br />\n<br />\n另外，唔好再用咁撚多色亂鳩咁highlight，你<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一段嘢</span>用多過<span style=\"color: red;\">三隻色</span>，我已經唔知你<span style=\"color: blue;\">重點</span>想講咩，唔期望大家識整靚張嘢或者張嘢望落似設計過，但屌你最基本都要有個grid system啦，排到咁亂點撚樣睇啊，自己google下咩係grid system。<br />\n<br />\npropaganda就係branding，如果你唔識，你可以係同一類嘅宣傳用死同一種template，例如：<br />\n批評政府係黑底白字加grid system 1；<br />\n上街活動係白底黑字加grid system 2，等等。<br />\n只要你各類夠統一，同埋不斷重複，啲人就會認住你個template，識得搵佢要睇嘅嘢嚟睇。如果你識設計（唔撚係識design software）可以不理。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n二<br />\n<br />\n籌錢做印刷，具體點實行唔知，文宣要快，要多，印刷費就唔會少得過前線買裝備嘅錢，呢個係事實，係咁。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n有其他問題就問。"},{"pid":"a8c1376b9a397d615fe06dbc1fdc921b0305bac5","tid":1442084,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T22:53:40.000Z","msg":"飛機post就多，有問題就無人面對"},{"pid":"23faa91c9ad4c8f30b79b059d844afc58426a687","tid":1442084,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:03:46.000Z","msg":"文宣密密做 落場手足可唔可以都幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑狗屌老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442071</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c8b9f887b0d6452175f225f35d8a01665b57739b","tid":1442084,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:12:09.000Z","msg":"［藍絲文宣方向第一波攻勢］打破舊有思想：共產黨好撚強大<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3164d477347dac14b60149d8dcb7932fba8a3dd","tid":1442084,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/10/133552_e9d1b7ebb2c4cf740182e054e0b0d8e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2F133552_e9d1b7ebb2c4cf740182e054e0b0d8e9.png&h=8fab403d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/09/185004_49f1f9c80e6665caf001443abb1195bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F185004_49f1f9c80e6665caf001443abb1195bf.png&h=deacb561&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbdd7112e6fba449ba9dc049be0f26248006e16b","tid":1442084,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Srv487q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrv487q.jpg&h=d6367102&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5j5Ty7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5j5Ty7.jpg&h=22368039&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76c3fc1f2258c2a08af3f1328890d244328402cd","tid":1442084,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3164d477347dac14b60149d8dcb7932fba8a3dd","tid":1442084,"uid":202464,"like